# AVD-AWS-0104: Unrestricted egress on VPC endpoints and RDS security groups
# Accepted: private VPC, no internet gateway on affected subnets.
# Restricting egress requires maintaining AWS service CIDR lists.
AVD-AWS-0104

# AVD-AWS-0040: EKS public API endpoint enabled
# Accepted: portfolio project, no bastion/VPN. Private endpoint also enabled.
# Production would restrict to office CIDR or disable entirely.
AVD-AWS-0040

# AVD-AWS-0041: EKS public endpoint accessible from 0.0.0.0/0
# Same justification as AVD-AWS-0040 above.
AVD-AWS-0041
